# Secrets — NEVER commit. Real values live in Lovable Cloud → Secrets.
# Only `.env.example` (template, no real values) is allowed in git.
# Covers Kling (KLING_ACCESS_KEY / KLING_SECRET_KEY) and every other runtime
# secret documented in docs/ENV.md and docs/KLING_SECRETS.md.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.env
*.env.local
secrets.json
secrets.*.json
kling.json
kling.*.json
**/kling-credentials*
